What You Need To Know About Board Games
 From Erik Arneson, your Editor and Guide

 --------------------------- EDITOR'S NOTE ----------------------------
 If you're like me, you spend an inordinate amount of time reading the promotional text found on game boxes. And if you do that, you'll be great at our "Name That Game" game going on in the About Board Games Forum!
 http://boardgames.about.com
 ------------------------- IN THE SPOTLIGHT ---------------------------
 Name That Game
 What game box does this text come from? "When attacked by the walking dead, when your buddies' bodies get up to bite you, when the chain of command is not just broken but in tatters, here's what you do. Stick your head between your..." Join the game today.
 http://glclk.about.com/?zi=10/76P
